    {
      "id": "PopularPost259186",
      "post_content": "I distinctly remember the first booster of Invasion I opened up. I loved Mercadian Masques, loved Nemesis, loved Prophecy. I was sure I was going to love Invasion.   \n  \nIt was the only booster of Invasion I ever opened. Seeing this card in that pack confused me. I remember thinking \"is this a joke? Is this some kind of experimental token that they slipped in? AM I SUPPOSED TO CUT THIS IN HALF AND MAKE SOME KIND OF MINI DECK??????? YOU CANT HAVE TWO CARDS IN ONE. THIS. IS. STUPID.\" Seeing this \"card\" in that pack made me stop caring about magic for 8 years.  \n  \nI only recently decided to click on the Invasion Wikipedia article and read it for the first time. Sure enough split cards are mentioned there, as well as the fact that they were apparently disliked by the entire R&D team. In true Wikipedia fashion there is a link to an article verifying this, an article written by none other than Mark Rosewater. In it he explains how only three people stood up for split cards when they were called int... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "SarcasmElemental",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost259186\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">I distinctly remember the first booster of Invasion I opened up. I loved Mercadian Masques, loved Nemesis, loved Prophecy. I was sure I was going to love Invasion. <br/><br/>It was the only booster of Invasion I ever opened. Seeing this card in that pack confused me. I remember thinking \"is this a joke? Is this some kind of experimental token that they slipped in? AM I SUPPOSED TO CUT THIS IN HALF AND MAKE SOME KIND OF MINI DECK??????? YOU CANT HAVE TWO CARDS IN ONE. THIS. IS. STUPID.\" Seeing this \"card\" in that pack made me stop caring about magic for 8 years.<br/><br/>I only recently decided to click on the Invasion Wikipedia article and read it for the first time. Sure enough split cards are mentioned there, as well as the fact that they were apparently disliked by the entire R&amp;D team. In true Wikipedia fashion there is a link to an article verifying this, an article written by none other than Mark Rosewater. In it he explains how only three people stood up for split cards when they were called int... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 259186)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '259186'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy85318\">SarcasmElemental</span>\r\n                                (7/24/2012 1:16:00 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
